'''格哈德·多馬克'''（'''Gerhard Johannes Paul Domagk'''，{{bd|1895年|10月30日|1964年|4月24日|catIdx=Domagk, Gerhard}}）是一位[[德國|德國]][[病理學|病理學家]]與[[細菌學|細菌學家]]。

==生平==
出生於德國[[布蘭登堡邦|布蘭登堡邦]]。多馬克由於發現了能有效對抗細菌感染的藥物[[百浪多息|百浪多息]]，而獲得了1939年的[[諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎|諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎]]。不過卻由於[[納粹|納粹]]政權的強迫而拒絕獲獎，並於一週後遭[[蓋世太保|蓋世太保]]逮捕<ref>Thomas Hager, ''The Demon Under the Microscope'' (2006) ISBN 1400082137 (cited in [http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=6667754 "The Saga of a Sulfa Drug Pioneer"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=6667754 |date=20090309204315 }} - [[NPR|NPR]] ''[[Weekend_Edition|Weekend Edition]]'' [[23_December|23 December]], 2006)</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/nobelprize_facts.html |title=NobelPrize.org |access-date=2007-10-18 |archive-date=2007-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070202025710/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/nobelprize_facts.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NobelBook">
{{cite book
 | last = Schück
 | first = Henrik
 | coauthors = Ragnar Sohlman, Anders Österling, Göran Liljestrand, Arne Westgren, Manne Siegbahn, August Schou, Nils K. Ståhle
 | editor = [[Nobel_Foundation|Nobel Foundation]]
 | title = Nobel: The Man and His Prizes
 | year = 1950
 | publisher = Klara Civiltryckeri
 | location = Stockholm
 | pages = 167-179
 | chapter = The Prize in Physiology and Medicine: The Nobel Prizes in Wartime
}}</ref>。這是由於先前一名納粹批判者[[卡爾·馮·奧西茨基|卡爾·馮·奧西茨基]]（Carl von Ossietzky）獲[[諾貝爾和平獎|諾貝爾和平獎]]，使當時的德國政府制定了不允許接受諾貝爾獎的法律<ref name="NobelBook">
{{cite book
 | last = Schück
 | first = Henrik
 | coauthors = Ragnar Sohlman, Anders Österling, Göran Liljestrand, Arne Westgren, Manne Siegbahn, August Schou, Nils K. Ståhle
 | editor = [[Nobel_Foundation|Nobel Foundation]]
 | title = Nobel: The Man and His Prizes
 | year = 1950
 | publisher = Klara Civiltryckeri
 | location = Stockholm
 | pages = 167-179
 | chapter = The Prize in Physiology and Medicine: The Nobel Prizes in Wartime
}}</ref>。 直到[[戰後|戰後]]的1947年，多馬克才正式接受了諾貝爾獎。

多马克于1959年成为英国[[皇家学会|皇家学会]]的外籍院士；他的简短的传记是由英国皇家学会于1964年出版<ref name="frs">{{Cite journal | last1 = Colebrook | first1 = Leonard| authorlink = Leonard Colebrook| doi = 10.1098/rsbm.1964.0003 | title = Gerhard Domagk 1895-1964 | journal = [[Biographical_Memoirs_of_Fellows_of_the_Royal_Society|Biographical Memoirs of Fellows of the Royal Society]] | volume = 10 | pages = 38–26 | year = 1964 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref>。

